     * 
     * It is possible to add additional descriptors to a [MediaStreamSource](mediastreamsource.md) after it has been created, by invoking the [AddStreamDescriptor](mediastreamsource_addstreamdescriptor_503977765.md) method.
     * @param {IMediaStreamDescriptor} descriptor The [AudioStreamDescriptor](audiostreamdescriptor.md) or [VideoStreamDescriptor](videostreamdescriptor.md) to create the [MediaStreamSource](mediastreamsource.md) from.
     * @returns {MediaStreamSource} 
     * @see https://learn.microsoft.com/uwp/api/windows.media.core.mediastreamsource.#ctor
     */
    static CreateFromDescriptor(descriptor) {
        if (!MediaStreamSource.HasProp("__IMediaStreamSourceFactory")) {
