     * @param {IMediaStreamDescriptor} descriptor The first [AudioStreamDescriptor](audiostreamdescriptor.md) or [VideoStreamDescriptor](videostreamdescriptor.md) to create the [MediaStreamSource](mediastreamsource.md) from.
